adband communications devices marvell plans to recruit significant additional engineering resources including design engineers and product and test engineers over the next few years to further support this effort mapl headquarters is also chartered with the management of the companys asia pacific sales offices including taiwan and japan in addition to ic design and development mapl will concentrate on sales customer service manufacturing operations finance and administration it and human resources efforts opening a regional headquarters and a cuttingedge technology design center in singapore is a logical next step for marvell in its quest for global expansion singapore is a semiconductor hub that offers many benefits including an excellent business environment and communications infrastructure a central location and semiconductor manufacturing fabrication support said dr sehat sutardja marvell technology group ltds president and ceo with our stateoftheart design center and technology expertise marvell will support the growth of the technical talent base in the region stated dr hoo kuong managing director of mapl our facility will also support the increased demand for marvells communications ics and will continue to streamline our design and manufacturing efficiencies speaking at the ceremony about the manpower capabilities for the industry mr teo ming kian cochairman of the economic development board said edb has introduced two manpower initiatives to boost the manpower supply to this growing industry namely the specialist manpower program for ic design and the postgraduate manpower program to match the industrys needs for manpower edb is currently working with the universities research institutes and research centers on new manpower initiatives to supply an additional  ic designers over the next three years for this industry the new design center is located at  lorong chuan  new tech park singapore  for assistance call   or visit marvells web site at wwwmarvellcom the opening of the new office and design center in singapore marks another significant milestone in marvells history and provides evidence of the companys continued commitment to meet the increasing needs for highbandwidth communication ics added dr sutardja in august marvell set the industry direction with the worlds first and only  micron alaska™ gigabit ethernet over copper devices in volume production today in september marvell introduced the industrys first systemonchip soc platform to satisfy requirements of the entire data storage market the company also completed its initial public offering on june   the strongest ipo for the second quarter of  marvell is also the recipient of many accolades including outstanding supplier award from several high profile customers and outstanding financial performance by the fabless semiconductor association about marvell marvell comprises marvell technology group ltd mtgl and its subsidiaries marvell semiconductor inc msi marvell asia pte ltd mapl and marvell japan kk mjkk on behalf of mtgl msi designs develops and markets integrated circuits utilizing proprietary communications mixedsignal processing cmsp and digital signal processing technologies for broadband communicationsrelated and data storage markets mapl is headquartered in singapore and is responsible for marvells production and distribution operations as used in this release the terms company and marvell refer to the entire group of companies the companys proprietary cmsp technology combines custom digital signal processing algorithms to allow technology customers to store and move digital data on demand at high data access rates the company initially focused its core technology on the data storage market the company more recently applied its technology to the high speed or broadband data communications market by introducing products that are used in network access equipment to provide the interface between communications systems and data transmission media msi is